works.description: If you are on the hunt for some distinctive outdoor furniture units, you might want to consider this daybed. One of the many beautiful and timeless designs from the German outdoor furniture company Solpuri, the Lagoon daybed makes for wonderful and relaxing moments in the open air. The beach chair/bed comes complete with awnings and LED lighting in different colors. Designed by Klaus Nolting, the ergonomically shaped Solpuri Lagoon daybed rotates to offer protection against sunburn whilst providing shade. The waterproof handmade deck is made of polyethylene.
